<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440087>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–22. Holocynips hartmani, asexual female: 17, head, frontal view. 18, antenna. 19, mesosoma and propleura, frontal view. 20, mesosoma, dorsal view. 21, metascutellum and propodeum, posterodorsal view. 22, metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440087/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440089>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23–29. Andricus quercuscalifornicus, asexual female: 23–24, head: 23, frontal view, 24, posterior view. 25–27, mesosoma: 25, dorsal view, 26, dorsal view, anterior part, 27, lateral view. 28, metascutellum and propodeum, posterodorsal view. 29, metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440089/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440091>
    dc:description "FIGURES 30–36. Disholcaspis costaricensis, asexual female: 30, head, frontal view. 31, mesosoma, lateral view, 32, mesoscutum, dorsal view. 33, mesoscutellum, dorsal view. 34, metascutellum and propodeum, posterodorsal view. 35, metasoma, lateral view. 36, ventral spine of hypopygium, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440081>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Protobalandricus spectabilis, female: 1–3, head: 1, frontal view, 2, posterior view, 3, dorsal view. 4, antenna. 5, hind leg. 6, forewing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440081/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440083>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–11. Protobalandricus spectabilis, female: 7, mesosoma and propleura, frontal view. 8–10, mesosoma: 8, lateral view, 9, dorsal view, 10, dorsal view, anterior part. 11, metascutellum and propodeum, posterodorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440083/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440085>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–16. Protobalandricus spectabilis: 12–14, metasoma, female: 12, general, lateral view, 13, part, lateral view, 14, ventral spine of hypopygium, ventral view. 15–16, gall (photos by J. Nicholls): 15, fresh mature gall, 16, previous year’s gall with emergence holes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1440085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

